<p>As SRCCON approaches, here’s everything you need to know to prepare for the conference and get setup. Once SRCCON is up and running, you’ll spend most of your time on our <a href="/signin">SRCCON 2022 Participant HQ on Eventbrite</a>, and in our conference Slack.</p>

