      <p>SRCCON will have direct Zoom links for all our talks, sessions, and meetups, and we can create more of them as you sign up to lead your own meetups. All direct Zoom links will be posted on both <a href="/signin/">our Eventbrite page</a> and in our Slack.</p>
    </div>
